# Naming Conventions

## Folder names

- Format: `{language}-{framework}` in kebab-case
- Without framework: `{language}` only (e.g. `rust`, `go`)
- Variants: add a descriptive suffix (e.g. `python-fastapi-crud`, `python-fastapi-auth`)

## Examples

- `go`
- `python-fastapi`
- `typescript-bun`
- `rust-axum`
- `python-fastapi-websocket`
